flowchart TB
  SDK[Browser SDK<br/>existing contract] --> Edge[CloudFront + regional intake API<br/>Node/Python workers]
  Edge --> Validate[Schema validation<br/>tenant auth<br/>idempotency key]
  Validate --> KDS[Kinesis Data Streams<br/>durable intake]
  Validate --> DLQ[SQS dead-letter queue<br/>bad schema / auth failures]

  KDS --> Flink[Managed Apache Flink<br/>dedupe + sessionization + aggregates]
  Flink --> Hot[DynamoDB hot aggregates<br/>tenant + metric + time bucket]
  Flink --> Redis[Redis behavior state<br/>personalization triggers]
  Flink --> S3[S3 raw + normalized event lake<br/>partitioned by tenant/date]
  S3 --> Athena[Athena / Glue catalog<br/>audit and validation queries]
  S3 --> Export[Customer warehouse exports<br/>Snowflake / BigQuery batch]
  Hot --> Dashboard[Real-time dashboards<br/>freshness SLO]
  Redis --> Personalize[Personalization decision API]

  Control[PostgreSQL control plane<br/>tenants, schemas, export config] --> Edge
  Control --> Flink
  Control --> Export

  Delete[GDPR/CCPA deletion request] --> Tombstone[Deletion tombstone + workflow]
  Tombstone --> Redis
  Tombstone --> Hot
  Tombstone --> S3
  Tombstone --> Export
  Tombstone --> Audit[Deletion audit log]

  Observe[CloudWatch + data quality checks] --> Edge
  Observe --> KDS
  Observe --> Flink
  Observe --> Hot
  Observe --> Export

